	* ange-ftp.el (ange-ftp-hash-mark-msgs): Make match more general.

Thu Dec 16 16:44:02 1993  Karl Berry  (karl@cs.umb.edu)

	* compile.el (grep-command): New variable.
	(grep): Use it.

